Type Combos

Normal/Ice
Takes x4 from fighting
Takes x2 from rock, steel and fire
Takes Neutral Damage from Normal, Flying, Poison, Ground, Bug, Water, Grass, Electric, Psychic, Dragon, Dark and Fairy
Takes x1/2 from Ice
Immunity to Ghost

Normal/Bug
Takes x2 from Flying, Rock and Fire
Takes Neutral Damage from Normal, Fighting, Poison, Bug, Steel, Water, Electric, Psychic, Ice, Dragon, Dark and Fairy
Takes x1/2 from Ground and Grass
Immunity to Ghost

Normal/Rock
Takes x4 from fighting
Takes x2 from Ground, Steel, Water and Grass
Takes Neutral Damage from Rock, Bug, Electric, Psychic, Ice, Dragon, Dark and Fairy
Takes x1/2 from Normal, Flying, Poison and Fire
Immunity to ghost

Fire/Fairy
Takes x2 from Poison, Ground, Rock and Water
Takes Neutral Damage from Normal, Flying, Ghost, Steel, Electric and Psychic
Takes x1/2 from Fighting, Fire, Grass, Ice, Dark and Fairy
Takes x1/4 from Bug
Immunity to Dragon

Normal/steel
Takes x4 from fighting
Takes x2 from Ground and Fire
Takes Neutral Damage from Water, Electric and Dark
Takes x1/2 damage from Normal, Flying, Rock, Bug, Steel, Grass, Psychic, Ice, Dragon and Fairy
Immunity to Poison and Ghost

Bug/Dragon
Takes x2 from Flying, Rock, Ice, Dragon and Fairy
Takes Neutral Damage from Normal, Poison, Bug, Ghost, Steel, Fire, Psychic and Dark
Takes x1/2 from Fighting, Ground, Water and Electric
Takes x1/4 from Grass
